Events.Summary: Shooting incident at Gelatogalore. Gunshots fired, cop killed, black van involved. Chaos and fear in the Gelatogalore parking lot.
Police officer shot during a shooting incident. Officer in good condition. Additional police units dispatched. Ambulance on scene.
Biker hit by a vehicle. Coffee shop owner cheered him up with a coffee. Police cornered the erratic driver.
Community rising up against the system. Cops scared of the power of the people. Calls for change and activism.
